      <p><i class='bx bx-time-five'></i>Monday to Friday - 24H/24H</p>
      <p><i class='bx bx-time-five'></i>Saturday and Sunday - 7am to 3pm</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-right">
      <h1>Get In Touch</h1>
      <p>Benin, Cotonou / Abomey-Calavi<i class='bx bx-map-pin'></i></p>
      <p>afrikshop@website.com <i class='bx bxl-google-plus'></i></p>
      <p>+229 00272552 <i class='bx bx-phone'></i></p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="social-links">
    <i class='bx bxl-facebook'></i>
